      "changelog": "Vonix-Network NeoForge 1.21.1 LuckPerms backport.\n\n## What this is\nA NeoForge 1.21.1 build of LuckPerms with:\n1. **Imagineer7's capability-init fixes** ([source](https://github.com/Imagineer7/LuckPerms_Custom_Fixes/releases/tag/5.4.145)) — resolves `IllegalStateException: Capability has not been initialised` race vs Balm/FTB Ranks during player join (LP upstream issues [#4183](https://github.com/LuckPerms/LuckPerms/issues/4183) / [#4235](https://github.com/LuckPerms/LuckPerms/issues/4235))\n2. **41 upstream commits backported** from luckperms/master onto the last MC 1.21.1-compatible base (`136a4859f`). Highlights:\n   - Redis Sentinel support (#4244)\n   - NATS auth token support (#4238)\n   - Common placeholders module (#4267)\n   - SQL Messenger time-column index (#4255)\n   - Verbose chat rate-limit\n   - SqlStorage duplicate readNode fix\n   - UUID mismatch warning suppression (#4194)\n   - IPv6 support\n   - Adventure 4.17\n   - User Housekeeper timeout bump\n   - Many more — see [BACKPORT-LOG.md](https://github.com/Vonix-Network/LuckPerms/blob/vonix-neoforge-fixes/BACKPORT-LOG.md)\n\n## Target\n- Minecraft: **1.21.1**\n- NeoForge: **21.1.x** (tested on 21.1.215)\n- Java: **21** (class file version 65 — works on yolks java_21 and java_25)\n\n## Verified\nBoot-tested locally on `servercheap` with NeoForge 21.1.215 + Java 21:\n- ✅ Standalone boot: `Successfully enabled`, PermissionAPI registered, clean `Done(`\n- ✅ Boot with Balm 21.0.59 + FTB Ranks 2101.1.3 + FTB Library 2101.1.32 + Architectury 13.0.8 — the exact mod set that crashed Protocol Zero / Stone Block 4 on stock LP 5.4.140: no `Capability has not been initialised`, FTB Ranks loaded its rank tree from LP cleanly.\n\n## Skipped from upstream\n5 commits unportable to the 1.21.1 base (Hytale-only, Folia-only, or hard-coupled to post-1.21.1 shared modules). Full log: BACKPORT-LOG.md.\n\n## Credits\n- Original mod: [Luck](https://github.com/LuckPerms/LuckPerms) under MIT\n- Capability-init fixes: [Imagineer7](https://github.com/Imagineer7/LuckPerms_Custom_Fixes)\n- Backport + Vonix build: Vonix Network",
